{
  "stem": "27031.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And you were scared to walk on the street when the Germans came in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were always hiding in the house.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after that, they put us in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "It wasn't a fenced in ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They put us-- they took two Jewish streets and packed in all the Jews from the whole town into that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Also, they brought in other Jews from the smaller villages or farms, brought them into that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So things were cramped, very, very cramped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No name.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Werba ghetto, that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We could, because there was no fences.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But after the Germans came in, they set up a local militia.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were pro-Nazi.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Pro-Nazi, and, uh, and, uh, in some cases, they were worse than the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they knew the Jewish population.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They knew them by first name, by name, by last name.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were a little harder on us than the Nazis.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Also the parents, I can remember, they pointed out to us that if you see Gestapo-- that was an elite German Nazi troop-- and they were-- and the Gestapo is the one that used to come and kill the Jews.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So they pointed out to us, if you see Gestapo, run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Local Polish population, they were in the same position as us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It's the Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This is Ukraine, and when the Nazis come in, the Poles weren't any longer.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was Ukrainian Nazi supporters.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were-- they were not treated well, but treated much better than the Jews.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They weren't killed, but they were, um, mistreated in a way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because the Polish government, they were ruling the Ukrainians, and then the Ukrainians started ruling and they mistreated the Poles.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Vice versa.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were, because there was no fences.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
